text: Nikolay Bauman () is a 1967 Soviet drama movie directed by Semyon Tumanov.Всесильная женщинаНИКОЛАЙ БАУМАН It stars Rodion Aleksandrov, Elina Bystritskaya, and Igor Dmitriev. == Actors == * Rodion Aleksandrov as Zotov * Elina Bystritskaya as Andreyeva * Igor Dmitriev as Kachalov * Yefim Kopelyan as Morozov * Igor Ledogorov as Nikolay Bauman * Irina Miroshnichenko as Nadya == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet movies Category:1967 movies Category:Soviet drama movies
